<item>
            <title>[AMQ-6665] certificate-based authentication on network bridge fails for nio+ssl protocol</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6665</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;client certificate authentication works in the following scenario:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Broker A
    ...
    &amp;lt;jaasDualAuthenticationPlugin 
        configuration=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;activemq&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        sslConfiguration=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;CertLogin&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
    ...
    &amp;lt;transportConnector name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;sslTransportConnector&quot;&lt;/span&gt; uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ssl:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//0.0.0.0:61618?needClientAuth=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&amp;amp;amp;wantClientAuth=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Broker B&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    ...
    networkConnector uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//(ssl://localhost:61618)&quot;&lt;/span&gt; name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;myNetworkConnector&quot;&lt;/span&gt; duplex=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; consumerTTL=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2&quot;&lt;/span&gt; messageTTL=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;100&quot;&lt;/span&gt; dynamicOnly=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;    ...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But if you change the transport to nio+ssl, the network connector fails with the following message:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;INFO | Stopping vm:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//localhosta#0 because Failed with SecurityException: User name [&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;] or password is invalid.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
