                            <comment id="15986375" author="gtully" created="Thu, 27 Apr 2017 11:10:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;issue was nio+ssl transport not extending SslTtransport but since &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-6339&quot; title=&quot;AMQP: Add support for AMQP over WebSockets&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AMQ-6339&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AMQ-6339&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; the relevant getPeerCerts is pushed back to tcpTransport. Now checking for that in the network bridge&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
